{
  "stem": "5644.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mine information-- mine observation was that the Jewish boy, which was the Kazik, Kazik, only the information which I set to the museum in Israel, and when I said Kazik, one of the people which know about the happening there, which he wrote a book about it, said, I think that you are right.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was the name, Kazik, because we know another name.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But that was Kazik.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We know now.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kazik was a young boy, and the story goes that his father and mother have been taken to Ravensbruck.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the beginning, everybody was taken from Poles, and killed in Ravensbruck.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he's the son of the people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he got-- he's the janitor of this building.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of Number 6.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the beauty of it was that the Poles there didn't know the janitor before, because that was a Jewish place.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not a Christian place.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Poles came in when the Jews had been thrown of Muranowska.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So this story went out beautifully.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's strictly mine opinion that he was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I must say that I didn't--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Didn't have any proof of it, nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was the one watching everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now Karski came in there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I brought Karski in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was the first one to walk, and in the back was another boy to walk, to get him in to the other side.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When we brought him inside, he hit his head on the pipe, and he said a very, very bad Polish swearing word.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said that he didn't have to bow that low even in the church or something, like he did have to bow his head here.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A very [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then he came out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we came out, number 7 9.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And two people have been waiting there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "ZOB.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, ZOB.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "ZOB.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
